    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      73.08,
      71.46,
      296.77,
      131.02
    ],
    "text": "B. These are collections of articles about current events usually published daily. Since there is at least one in every city, it is a great source of local information.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      193.68,
      184.59,
      446.89,
      229.75
    ],
    "text": "C. These cover virtually any topic, fact or fiction. This is one of the most common sources of information used by many people.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      83.16,
      284.23,
      356.9,
      358.18
    ],
    "text": "D. These are collections of short, factual entries. There are two types of these called general and subject. General ones provide overviews on a wide variety of topics while the others contain in-depth entries focusing on one field of study.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      213.48,
      391.58,
      453.02,
      465.53
    ],
    "text": "E. This allows you to access information on the Internet through a browser. One of the main features of this is speed. This contains information beyond plain text. It includes sounds, images, and video.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      71.5,
      510.52,
      305.29,
      541.28
    ],
